title: Unearthed - AfterDark Horrorfest
description:
A vicious creature that&#039;s been trapped for 900 years get unearthed during an archaeological dig in the middle of a desolate town.  As the carnage escalates, the local sheriff and a ground of stranded civilians must find a way to destroy the creature that only has one mission - complete annihilation.

This is my second release of the 03/08 AfterDark collection.  The file runs a bit short of 300 MB because I&#039;ve removed all of the trailers (quicker for you to get it running).
